articles.title: Queen guitarist May, soccer Lionesses named in king's New Year honours - RNZ
articles.description: Britain recognised Queen guitarist Brian May, several English "Lionesses" who won the European women's soccer championship and diplomats involved in the response to Russia's invasion of Ukraine in King Charles' first New Year's honours list.
